    "updated_at": "2016-02-02T09:45:29Z",
    "body": "yes it works , my code is:\n\n```\n    if (process.argv[1] == '--squirrel-firstrun') {\n        setTimeout(()=> {\n            autoUpdater.checkForUpdates();\n        }, 3000)\n    } else {\n        autoUpdater.checkForUpdates();\n    }\n```\n\nbut just wait for 3 seconds is not graceful, since we don't know when will it finish.\n\nit's better to check squirrel process running in checkForUpdates internally.\n\nor at least, document it in autoUpdater.\n"
